org.openimaj.rdf.serialize

Annotation Type RelationList


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface RelationList
    An annotation that marks a member of a class that must be an instance of Collection> to be treated specially during serialisation. When it is encountered, the relations stored in the list will be added to the graph without validation. The first object in the pair should be the predicate URI and the second object will be serialised by the RDFSerializer to its own subgraph.

    For example: 

                    class MyObject
                {
    Version:
    $Author$, $Revision$, $Date$
    Author:
    David Dupplaw (dpd@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
    Created:
    16 Nov 2012
